Package: AutoWD
Title: Automatically Set Working Directory
Version: 0.2
Authors@R: person("Hafsteinn", "Ragnarsson", email = "haffi921@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Automatically sets working directory to the active document's path.
    It is recommended that the user calls 'autowd()' in the beginning of the script
    before a data file is imported.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.4.3)
Imports: devtools,
    dirtools
Remotes: Haffi921/dirtools
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1.9000
